---
title: "_setReceiver (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_same: receiver == s_receiver
    q_check_same --> q_revert: true
    q_check_same --> q_set: false
    q_revert --> [*]: revert ValueNotUpdated()
    q_set --> q_emit: s_receiver = receiver
    q_emit --> [*]: emit ReceiverSet(receiver)

    note right of q_check_same
        INV-001: Setting same receiver is rejected (no-op prevention)
        INV-002: receiver can be set to address(0) to disable forwarding
    end note
